355
00:26:24,008 --> 00:26:29,227
Look, my brother-in-law,
evidence-wise, has nothing.

356
00:26:29,429 --> 00:26:31,730
He's operating on pure conjecture.

357
00:26:31,931 --> 00:26:34,648
And no one, not one person
that he works with...

358
00:26:34,850 --> 00:26:39,654
...thinks that you are anyone other
than an owner of a fast-food chain.

359
00:26:39,980 --> 00:26:42,115
But if something were to happen
to Hank?

360
00:26:42,315 --> 00:26:46,953
That would only draw their attention
to you and therefore, to me, as well.

361
00:26:47,319 --> 00:26:51,578
We have a mutual interest
in resolving this without violence.

362
00:26:52,657 --> 00:26:57,497
I will make sure
that he discovers nothing.

363
00:27:07,128 --> 00:27:08,136
Jesse!

364
00:27:08,754 --> 00:27:11,886
What? Oh, hey.
Don't wait to be, like, invited.

365
00:27:14,092 --> 00:27:15,895
Are we alone?

366
00:27:18,805 --> 00:27:21,652
- So where do we stand?
- Where do we stand on what?

367
00:27:21,849 --> 00:27:25,775
