371
00:27:34,985 --> 00:27:38,579
Asshole. You're creaming
to get it done, go do it yourself.

372
00:27:38,780 --> 00:27:42,078
If he didn't see me coming
like he's some kind of ...

373
00:27:42,992 --> 00:27:45,756
