that you want to be--

401
00:29:51,853 --> 00:29:55,815
No, that you need to be able
to be properly coached.

402
00:29:56,023 --> 00:29:58,111
Then, when you're near him...

403
00:29:58,484 --> 00:29:59,825
...you put this to use.

404
00:30:00,861 --> 00:30:04,242
Mike's just gonna tell me
to shut my mouth if I get busted.

405
00:30:04,447 --> 00:30:08,208
- He ain't gonna set up no meeting.
- Well, then insist on it, damn it!

406
00:30:08,493 --> 00:30:10,165
