415
00:31:55,543 --> 00:31:58,177
- Yes?
- I did some digging around.

416
00:31:58,379 --> 00:32:00,929
- And?
- Neither the DEA...

417
00:32:01,131 --> 00:32:04,180
...nor the APD considers you
a person of interest.

418
00:32:04,384 --> 00:32:07,231
