for the Mexican palate.

478
00:37:01,306 --> 00:37:05,945
I bet we like a little more chili
than you Chileans.

479
00:37:06,477 --> 00:37:10,949
We Mexicans like a good hard kick!

480
00:37:18,071 --> 00:37:21,416
